&quot;Enjoy a summer evening under the shade of old trees and with a wide view over meadows to the forest&quot;, the organizers emphasize the fantastic view.
The serenade takes place only in dry weather.
The organizers are hoping for many supporters to preserve the historic St. Hilarius complex, which is important for Tumlingen and Hörschweiler.
